{
  "stem": "833.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I memorized it in-- on one day of-- on one trip.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I have quite a good memory.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I can memorize things very-- especially if somebody tells it to me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I think it was two or three days later, I-- I sang it to him.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he says, oh, that sounds good to me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then I taught it to one of the musicians.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they accompanied to-- to guitars.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then we left to Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that's all I knew about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But many-- there's a peculiar thing of-- of some things.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I just wrote it for the people-- some kind of resistance, sometimes to give them hope and-- but if things begin to arouse the imagination of people-- whatever it is-- they begin to have their own life.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think 'Dachau'-- the 'Dachau Song' had-- had its own life without-- without me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Without its-- and lived by the word of mouth-- from-- from east to west, from south to north, in every concentration camp and later also in Russia.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I-- the numbers of-- of-- of arrangements I got were very peculiar.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, see, the-- yeah, cleaning-- cleaning of the latrines.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You see, in-- in Buchenwald, the really horrifying thing was that there was no water.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Absolutely no water, period.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't have any water.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We couldn't wash.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We couldn't have-- cleaning our teeth.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was no-- we couldn't clean anything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was no water.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So therefore, there were no toilets.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There were only open latrines.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That means deep-- deep ditches that you have-- there were some wood planks on-- on side of it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That's where people did their business.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And, of course, when you think that there were 10,000 people in all the [INAUDIBLE], there would only two or three latrines there.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
